 <p class="text-xs text-content-muted mt-1">Crea moldes de equipo para cargarlos rÃ¡pidamente.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="flex gap-2">
 <button type="button" id="btn-tb-cancelar" class="p-2 sm:px-4 sm:py-2 text-content-muted hover:text-neutral :text-neutral-200 hover:bg-background :bg-neutral-800 rounded-xl transition-colors font-bold text-sm hidden sm:block">Cancelar</button>
 <button type="button" id="btn-tb-close" class="p-2 -mr-2 text-content-muted hover:text-neutral-700 :text-neutral-200 hover:bg-background :bg-neutral-800 rounded-full transition-colors sm:hidden">
